title: FIFA 16 +UPDATE 5-CRACKED-STEAMWORKS
description:
Description: 
FIFA 16 is an association football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by EA Sports for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, Xbox 360, Xbox One, Android and iOS. 

The game is the first in the FIFA series to include female players. It is also the first in which the players on the covers were chosen by popular vote, including the first women to appear on the cover. Martin Tyler and Alan Smith are the commentators for the game. 

Requirements: 

Minimum Requirements: 
CPU: Intel Core2 Quad Q6600 @ 2.4 Ghz (or AMD Phenom 7950 Quad-Core, AMD Athlon II X4 620 equivalent) 
RAM: 4 GB 
OS: Windows V/7/8/8.1 - 64-Bit 
Video Card: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 650 or AMD Radeon HD 5770 
Sound Card: Yes 
Free Disk Space: 15 GB 

Recommended Requirements: 
CPU: Intel i5-2550K @ 3.40GHz (or AMD FX-6350 Six-Core equivalent) 
RAM: 8 GB 
OS: Windows V/7/8/8.1 - 64-Bit 
Video Card: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 460 or AMD Radeon HD 6870 
Sound Card: Yes 
Free Disk Space: 15 GB 

How to start: 

Instructions: 

[The first run] 


1. Install Origin and log in to your account (if you dont have one - register). 
2. At the top click the tab "Origin" -> "Application Settings", and remove the checkbox "Automatically follow the updates of games." 
3. Tab "Shop" -> Free games -> Demo version, we find "the FIFA 16 Demo" and click "download", the game will appear in your library. Exit the client. 
4. Install FIFA.16.Update.5-Steamworks 
5. When we go in the Origin (on Dekstop) with you aacount, choose in the library "FIFA 16 Demo" and run. After exit the menu immediately. 

Once the game itself and origin MUST appear in the network, at this moment the game will be activated. Without it nothing will not work! 

P.S. If you have - "An update for FIFA 16 Demo", press "Play without updating." 

-------------------------------------------------- --------------------- 

[Next launches] 

- Shortcut "the FIFA 16" will always run your Origin in offline mode by clicking on it opens a window with your Origin username (but without password), enter the password. 
- Go to your library and run the "FIFA 16 Demo". Now run always through "FIFA 16 Demo" and in this way. Origin will think that you are playing in the demo version but this is full version) 

-------------------------------------------------- --------------------- 

Remarks: 
- Never check the hash. 
- Laucher does not change the resolution, it is done independently in the file "fifasetupfifasetup_default.ini" 

Strings: 
[Code] RESOLUTIONWIDTH = 1920 
RESOLUTIONHEIGHT = 1080 [/ code] 

FullHD is the default. 


- Improved physics and rules in order to achieve a more accurate judge's decisions. 
- Behavioral changes players when using the tactics of the ball, and the selection of high-pressure situations. 
- Realistic effects of fatigue by using tactics tackles. This will affect the ability to conduct high pressure during the match. 
- Improved avtootbor ball when defenders were positioned correctly in relation to the attacker. 
- Also improved positioning for better support and attacks. 

Also bonuses to attributes of players to teams with high teamwork in the Ultimate Team mode has been changed. This is primarily impact on the passes, interceptions, and long shots
